{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this happened a few times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then also, a few times, I guess the Polish people let us know that they are planning-- sometimes it was-- it was true.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes it was just, you know, it wasn't so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they let us know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we used to leave these places and go to-- you know, just go all night, next day, to much farther places, to-- to-- to leave these, you know, places where we were, you know, housing there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a few times, we were lucky because we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes they didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also, you know, certain times, we used to go down to the village-- I, and a few more that-- we had these people that we could stay there a couple nights, until-- [SIGHS] until there came a time that they were very angry, the-- the Ukrainians there.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was a Polish village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they knew that Jewish people are coming down and they are sort of helping us a little bit out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there was-- this-- this village was like a valley and then around, you know, you know, like-- I want to say mountains, but you know, hills.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they came from the surrounding-- from the Ukrainians' villages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They came on-- on these, you know, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] you know, so, like, Hanaczow was like a valley, and they try to-- to shoot down, and they-- [SIGHS] and that time, I was, and a few more of us, were also hidden in one of the bunkers there, on the house.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sudden they started a fire on this-- that they just burned the whole village, from all the sides, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
